				{"id":96754,"date":"2017-04-07T20:06:16","date_gmt":"2017-04-07T20:06:16","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/sharpspring.com\/?post_type=resource&#038;p=16754"},"modified":"2021-08-12T16:13:40","modified_gmt":"2021-08-12T20:13:40","slug":"bryton-case-study","status":"publish","type":"resource","link":"https:\/\/sharpspring.com\/resources\/bryton-case-study\/","title":{"rendered":"Proving ROI With Marketing Automation"},"content":{"rendered":"<p>[vc_row full_width=&#8221;stretch_row&#8221; gap=&#8221;20&#8243; content_placement=&#8221;middle&#8221; css=&#8221;.vc_custom_1504900143150{background-color: #13592d !important;}&#8221;][vc_column width=&#8221;1\/12&#8243;][\/vc_column][vc_column width=&#8221;2\/12&#8243;][vc_single_image image=&#8221;158475&#8243; img_size=&#8221;full&#8221;][\/vc_column][vc_column width=&#8221;2\/3&#8243;][vc_custom_heading text=&#8221;Using one platform to manage digital campaigns, score leads and nurture opportunities, resulting in 10x ROI.&#8221; font_container=&#8221;tag:h3|text_align:left|color:%23ffffff&#8221; google_fonts=&#8221;font_family:Open%20Sans%3A300%2C300italic%2Cregular%2Citalic%2C600%2C600italic%2C700%2C700italic%2C800%2C800italic|font_style:300%20light%20regular%3A300%3Anormal&#8221; css=&#8221;.vc_custom_1514078793249{margin-bottom: 30px !important;}&#8221;][\/vc_column][vc_column width=&#8221;1\/12&#8243;][\/vc_column][\/vc_row][vc_row full_width=&#8221;stretch_row&#8221; gap=&#8221;20&#8243; full_height=&#8221;yes&#8221; columns_placement=&#8221;top&#8221; equal_height=&#8221;yes&#8221; content_placement=&#8221;top&#8221; css=&#8221;.vc_custom_1513910633175{background-color: #f5f5f5 !important;}&#8221;][vc_column width=&#8221;1\/3&#8243;][vc_single_image image=&#8221;158476&#8243; alignment=&#8221;center&#8221;][vc_custom_heading text=&#8221;Demonstrated 10x ROI on all marketing efforts.&#8221; font_container=&#8221;tag:h3|text_align:center&#8221; use_theme_fonts=&#8221;yes&#8221; css=&#8221;.vc_custom_1508968226840{margin-bottom: 30px !important;}&#8221;][vc_column_text]With SharpSpring, Brytons had the tools to track, nurture and convert more leads and to zero in on high-performing keywords.[\/vc_column_text][\/vc_column][vc_column width=&#8221;1\/3&#8243;][vc_single_image image=&#8221;158477&#8243; alignment=&#8221;center&#8221;][vc_custom_heading text=&#8221;Increased sales conversions by 35%.&#8221; font_container=&#8221;tag:h3|text_align:center&#8221; use_theme_fonts=&#8221;yes&#8221; css=&#8221;.vc_custom_1508968251795{margin-bottom: 30px !important;}&#8221;][vc_column_text]Lead scoring in SharpSpring made phone and email campaigns convert at a higher rate.[\/vc_column_text][\/vc_column][vc_column width=&#8221;1\/3&#8243;][vc_single_image image=&#8221;158478&#8243; alignment=&#8221;center&#8221;][vc_custom_heading text=&#8221;Doing more of what\u2019s working.&#8221; font_container=&#8221;tag:h3|text_align:center&#8221; use_theme_fonts=&#8221;yes&#8221; css=&#8221;.vc_custom_1508968262643{margin-bottom: 30px !important;}&#8221;][vc_column_text]Brytons reallocated dollars to digital marketing to double down on AdWords campaigns that were killing it. With clear and compelling data to support results, Brytons decided to increase its marketing budget by 50%.[\/vc_column_text][\/vc_column][\/vc_row][vc_row css=&#8221;.vc_custom_1564515013308{margin-top: 0px !important;margin-bottom: 0px !important;padding-bottom: 0px !important;}&#8221;][vc_column width=&#8221;1\/12&#8243;][\/vc_column][vc_column width=&#8221;5\/6&#8243;]<div class=\" text-left\"><div class=\"m-b-30 custom-heading font-size-30px\"  ><h2 >Client<\/h2><span class=\"custom-heading-delim\" style=\"width:140px;\"><\/span><\/div><\/div>[vc_column_text]Brytons Home Improvement[\/vc_column_text][vc_empty_space height=&#8221;30px&#8221;]<div class=\" text-left\"><div class=\"m-b-30 custom-heading font-size-30px\"  ><h2 >Focus<\/h2><span class=\"custom-heading-delim\" style=\"width:140px;\"><\/span><\/div><\/div>[vc_column_text]Provides bathroom remodeling and window replacement services in North and South Carolina, USA.[\/vc_column_text][vc_empty_space height=&#8221;30px&#8221;]<div class=\" text-left\"><div class=\"m-b-30 custom-heading font-size-30px\"  ><h2 >Situation<\/h2><span class=\"custom-heading-delim\" style=\"width:140px;\"><\/span><\/div><\/div>[vc_column_text]Brytons uses a variety of channels to market its products, including home shows, showrooms, TV ads, email campaigns, AdWords, call centers and postcards. However, before using SharpSpring,the company didn\u2019t have a solid process for segmenting its leads and understanding their product interests. Brytons knew that the internet was bringing in a ton of leads, but it didn\u2019t know which ones were qualified. This made it difficult to track and prove the ROI of marketing campaigns and budget accordingly.[\/vc_column_text][vc_empty_space height=&#8221;30px&#8221;]<div class=\" text-left\"><div class=\"m-b-30 custom-heading font-size-30px\"  ><h2 >Goal<\/h2><span class=\"custom-heading-delim\" style=\"width:140px;\"><\/span><\/div><\/div>[vc_column_text]Prove the ROI of digital campaigns, effectively nurture leads until they are sales ready, and ensure the hottest leads are being worked.[\/vc_column_text]<div class=\"testimonial features-testimonial text-light  \"><div class=\"testimonial-description\"><p>``We had a record year last year when we started using SharpSpring. What we spend each month on marketing, we get back tenfold. That\u2019s our sweet spot right now, and we think this year will be even better.``<\/p>\n<\/div><div class=\"testimonial-image\"><h4>Kim Kinney<\/h4><p class=\"subtitle\">Director of Marketing, Brytons Home Improvement<\/p><\/div><\/div>[vc_empty_space height=&#8221;30px&#8221;]<div class=\" text-left\"><div class=\"m-b-30 custom-heading font-size-30px\"  ><h2 >Solution<\/h2><h5 class=\"\" >Brytons implemented SharpSpring with a focus on three key areas:<\/h5><span class=\"custom-heading-delim\" style=\"width:140px;\"><\/span><\/div><\/div>[vc_column_text]<strong>Google AdWords Native Integration<\/strong><br \/>\nAfter evaluating a number of keywords, the company was able to prove that the keyword phrase \u201cbathroom remodeling\u201d had the highest return on investment after its other branded keywords. \u201cBathroom remodeling\u201d is a very generic \u2013 and therefore very expensive \u2013 keyword, but SharpSpring helped prove that the cost per click was justified since these leads converted at the highest rate. Without this insight enabled by SharpSpring&#8217;s analytics, Brytons could have erroneously shifted budget to lower cost-per-lead keywords at the expense of higher converting keywords, thus lowering sales.<\/p>\n<p><strong>Lead Nurturing<\/strong><br \/>\nBrytons also used SharpSpring to improve its lead nurturing processes. Many leads were gathered during a remodel giveaway contest. Some had been engaging with Brytons for more than a year. They would click through emails, visit the site, and even spend up to 20 minutes on one particular page \u2013 but many of them were not buying. With SharpSpring, the company was able to track page visits to identify what these leads were looking for and then send a series of nurture emails to move them toward a purchase. Nurturing leads with helpful \u201cDid you know\u2026?\u201d and \u201cHow to\u2026\u201d emails helped Brytons gain the trust of its leads, so when the time came for them to make a purchase, Brytons was top of mind.<\/p>\n<p><strong>Lead Scoring<\/strong><br \/>\nUsing SharpSpring, Brytons was able to identify hot leads, which made it much easier to effectively pull lists for its call center and mailing campaigns. Each time a lead opened an email or visited a page on the website, his\/her lead score would go up, allowing Brytons to see who was engaged. SharpSpring offered insights on which pages and products leads were viewing, so Brytons could send more targeted messaging based on leads\u2019 interests.[\/vc_column_text]<div class=\"testimonial features-testimonial text-light  \"><div class=\"testimonial-description\"><p>``With SharpSpring, every time a lead opens an email or visits the website their score goes up, so we know that they are engaged. We also know what products they are interested in so that we can send more targeted messaging.``<\/p>\n<\/div><div class=\"testimonial-image\"><h4>Kim Kinney<\/h4><p class=\"subtitle\">Director of Marketing, Brytons Home Improvement<\/p><\/div><\/div>[vc_empty_space height=&#8221;30px&#8221;]<div class=\" text-left\"><div class=\"m-b-30 custom-heading font-size-30px\"  ><h2 >Real Results With SharpSpring<\/h2><span class=\"custom-heading-delim\" style=\"width:140px;\"><\/span><\/div><\/div><div class=\"icon-box effect text-color-dk-leaf-green large border\"  ><div class=\"icon\"  style=\"border-color:\"><i class=\"icon-graph\" ><\/i><\/div><p>Achieved a 10x return on marketing investment due to detailed insights into campaign performance and re-allocation of spend to higher-performing activities.<\/p>\n<\/div><div class=\"icon-box effect text-color-dk-leaf-green large border\"  ><div class=\"icon\"  style=\"border-color:\"><i class=\"icon-higher-value-relationships\" ><\/i><\/div><p>Increased leads by 35% as a result of targeted engagement with high lead scoring prospects and a streamlined sales process.<\/p>\n<\/div><div class=\"icon-box effect text-color-dk-leaf-green large border\"  ><div class=\"icon\"  style=\"border-color:\"><i class=\"icon-monthly-recurring-revenue\" ><\/i><\/div><p>Increased visibility and ROI on AdWords campaigns, justifying a 50% increase on marketing spend, which continues to show the same positive ROI.<\/p>\n<\/div><div class=\"testimonial features-testimonial text-light  \"><div class=\"testimonial-description\"><p>``Using SharpSpring, we were able to generate more quality leads, convert more leads to sales, and spend our marketing resources more wisely for an across-the-board impact. What's not to like about that? Any company not using a solid marketing automation platform is playing an old game and ignoring the new rules of the road. All companies should give serious consideration to SharpSpring. It\u2019s just smart business.``<\/p>\n<\/div><div class=\"testimonial-image\"><h4>Kim Kinney<\/h4><p class=\"subtitle\">Director of Marketing, Brytons Home Improvement<\/p><\/div><\/div>[vc_row_inner disable_element=&#8221;yes&#8221;][vc_column_inner width=&#8221;2\/3&#8243;][vc_column_text]<\/p>\n<div id=\"pgc-16754-9-0\" class=\"panel-grid-cell\">\n<div id=\"panel-16754-9-0-0\" class=\"so-panel widget widget_sow-editor panel-first-child panel-last-child\" data-index=\"15\">\n<div class=\"so-widget-sow-editor so-widget-sow-editor-base\">\n<div class=\"siteorigin-widget-tinymce textwidget\">\n<h2><strong>Interested in learning more?<\/strong><\/h2>\n<p>Adding marketing automation to your toolbox can help you grow your business. Schedule time with our Director of Partnerships to chat about your specific needs and see SharpSpring in action.<\/p>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<p>[\/vc_column_text][\/vc_column_inner][vc_column_inner width=&#8221;1\/3&#8243;][vc_btn title=&#8221;GET A DEMO&#8221; size=&#8221;lg&#8221; link=&#8221;url:https%3A%2F%2Fsharpspring.com%2Fget-a-demo%2F|title:GET%20A%20DEMO||&#8221;][\/vc_column_inner][\/vc_row_inner][vc_row_inner css=&#8221;.vc_custom_1513988782860{margin-top: 5% !important;border-top-width: 1px !important;border-top-color: #f5f5f5 !important;border-top-style: solid !important;}&#8221;][vc_column_inner width=&#8221;1\/3&#8243;][vc_single_image image=&#8221;158475&#8243; img_size=&#8221;full&#8221;][\/vc_column_inner][vc_column_inner width=&#8221;2\/3&#8243;][vc_column_text]Since 1992, Brytons Home Improvement has provided North and South Carolina with home remodeling services. All of its installers are employees, which allows them to work more efficiently and cost-effectively than other firms. Brytons prides itself on not giving estimates or quotes, only exact pricing. This way, there are no surprise costs or hidden fees, making it easier to build trust with customers.[\/vc_column_text][\/vc_column_inner][\/vc_row_inner][vc_row_inner css=&#8221;.vc_custom_1513988775296{margin-top: 3% !important;margin-bottom: 5% !important;border-top-width: 1px !important;border-top-color: #f5f5f5 !important;border-top-style: solid !important;}&#8221;][vc_column_inner width=&#8221;1\/3&#8243;]<a class=\"button button-3d full-rounded green\" href=\"\/all\/case-study\/\" target=\"_self\"  ><span>VIEW ALL CASE STUDIES<\/span><\/a>[\/vc_column_inner][vc_column_inner width=&#8221;2\/3&#8243;][vc_column_text]<\/p>\n<div id=\"pgc-16754-9-0\" class=\"panel-grid-cell\">\n<div id=\"panel-16754-9-0-0\" class=\"so-panel widget widget_sow-editor panel-first-child panel-last-child\" data-index=\"15\">\n<div class=\"so-widget-sow-editor so-widget-sow-editor-base\">\n<div class=\"siteorigin-widget-tinymce textwidget\">\n<div id=\"pgc-16754-11-0\" class=\"panel-grid-cell\">\n<div id=\"panel-16754-11-0-0\" class=\"so-panel widget widget_sow-editor panel-first-child panel-last-child\" data-index=\"20\">\n<div class=\"so-widget-sow-editor so-widget-sow-editor-base\">\n<div class=\"siteorigin-widget-tinymce textwidget\">\n<p>Hear directly from clients about how marketing automation is producing real-world results in a variety of industries.<\/p>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<div id=\"pgc-16754-11-1\" class=\"panel-grid-cell\"><\/div>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<p>[\/vc_column_text][\/vc_column_inner][\/vc_row_inner][\/vc_column][vc_column width=&#8221;1\/12&#8243;][\/vc_column][\/vc_row][vc_row full_width=&#8221;stretch_row_content_no_spaces&#8221; css=&#8221;.vc_custom_1513988534886{margin-top: 0px !important;padding-top: 0px !important;padding-bottom: 0px !important;}&#8221;][vc_column]<div class=\"jumbotron jumbotron-center background-dark text-light jumbotr